snippet: The 33-year-old may have been the oldest of the dozen American women at the Family Circle Cup, but she made it the furthest before being eliminated.
abstract: Venus Williams is ousted in women's third round of Family Circle Cup, losing to Eugenie Bouchard.
lead_paragraph: The 33-year-old may have been the oldest of the dozen American women at the Family Circle Cup, but she made it the furthest before being eliminated.

headline.main: Resilient Venus Williams Falls at Family Circle
